<div class="title_bar"><h1>About Scotty's Action Sport Network watersports and SUBA diving.</h1></div>
<div class="about-heading">Where is Scotty’s Action Sports Network?</div>
<div class="paragraph"> </div>
<div class="about-heading">How can I make a booking?</div>
<div class="paragraph">You may <a href="index.html">call us</a> direct or simply use our <a href="index.html">Contact form</a>. </div>
<div class="about-heading">Can I make a booking on the day of activity?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes, you can. But sometimes we cannot accommodate your preferred time.<br>
                    We strongly recommend you to make advance booking.<br>
                    There are no cancellation fees.</div>
<div class="about-heading">Can I change my booking on the day of activity?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes. Please check your booking before departure</div>
<div class="about-heading">Can I pay by card?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes (VISA, MasterCard, American Express, JCB). If you are staying at Shangri-La,  Hilton, or Plantation bay Resort and the activity is done within the resort, you may charge it to your room as well.</div>
<div class="about-heading">Should I wear swim suit before going to the Sea sports center?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes, but you can change in our restroom. </div>
<div class="about-heading">Can I join alone?</div>
<div class="paragraph">It depends on the activities. Island excursions and tube rides are minimum of two persons. If there are no other customers you have to pay for two.
                    Other activities such as scuba diving, parasailing, tow sports are minimum of one person only.</div>


<div class="title_bar">Scuba Diving </div>
<div class="about-heading">What should I bring?</div>
<div class="paragraph">If you are a licensed diver, please bring a Certification card, log books and some of your own dive equipment.<br>
<br>
If you are not licensed, just wear swim suit and come down to the center. </div>

<div class="about-heading">Never tried before can I enjoy?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes you can.  You can try <a href="../scuba_diving/courses/recreational/dsd.html">discover scuba diving (DSD)</a> or <a href="../scuba_diving/courses/recreational/openwater.html">open water diver</a> licenses course. </div>
  <div class="about-heading">I am wearing contact lenses or wearing  eye glasses.</div>
<div class="paragraph">We have some prescription masks. But there are limited. We recommend to book it for advance.</div>
<div class="about-heading">I have a license but my friend doesn’t. Can we dive together?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes you can.  You may join in while your friend does the pool session training or you can wait for the actual ocean dive, alternatively you can book for an exclusive  boat for an extra charge.</div>

<div class="about-heading">Can my family ride a boat with me and other divers?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes they can. And you may rent our snorkeling set, alternatively you can book for an exclusive  boat for an extra charge.</div>
<div class="title_bar">Parasailing </div>

<div class="about-heading">Can we get wet?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes you can. But if you don’t want to get wet, please let us know. We can cancel touch and go.</div>

<div class="about-heading">Can I bring camera up in the air?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes you can but if it's not water proof we recommend to leave it on land.  We can take  pictures for you from the boat and save  them on a CD for 500 pesos. </div>
<div class="about-heading">What is touch and go?</div>
<div class="paragraph">While you are flying you go down slowly touching the water   at about waist level.<br>
It is very exciting.</div>
<div class="about-heading">Can I ride  together with a friend?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes you can.</div>
<div class="title_bar"> Island Excursions </div>
<div class="about-heading">What should I bring?</div>
<div class="paragraph">The tour includes life jacket, snorkel set, fins, towel. We recommend to bring you own sun protection and camera.</div>
<div class="about-heading">Can I hire the boat only for  my family? </div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes, you can. You can have an exclusive boat for an extra charge. </div>
<div class="about-heading">How long to get to the island?</div>
<div class="paragraph"> These are from the hotel to the island, it depends on the weather condition.<br>
<ol>
  <li>Nalusuan - 40 minutes</li>
  <li>              Stilt restaurant - 40 minutes</li>
  <li>              Pandanon Island - 50 minutes</li>
  <li> Nalusuan island to pandanon island - 40 minutes</li>
  <li> Bohol Island - 1 hour.
  </li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="title_bar">Tow Sports </div>
<div class="about-heading">What should I bring?</div>
<div class="paragraph">We have life jacket and equipment. Just wear a swim suit and bring sun protection.</div>
<div class="about-heading">It's my first time to try.</div>
<div class="paragraph">No need to worry. We will teach you how to enjoy the activity.</div>
<div class="about-heading">Can you take pictures?</div>
<div class="paragraph">Yes we can. We can take  pictures for you, from the boat and save  them on a CD for 500 pesos. </div>
